        <h2>Before you choose Canary Pro</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="cp-faq__list">
        <details open>
          <summary><span>What makes Canary Pro different from the original Canary?</span></summary>
          <p>Canary Pro keeps the hybrid Canary idea but rebuilds it around a 14-driver matrix, quad electrostatic super tweeters, dual isobaric dynamic woofers, and a Super-Low Flat Impedance network for more consistent source pairing.</p>
